{
  "texts": [
    "Emulating the ZPD requires a complex, adaptive system capable of real-time assessment and responsiveness to a learner's changing needs.",
    "While ChatGPT can provide information and answer questions based on its training data, it lacks the capability to continuously measure a learner's understanding or to adjust its responses to maintain the delicate balance necessary for effective operation within a learner's ZPD (Isaac et al., 2023).",
    "While ChatGPT can provide a degree of personalized responses and educational support, it currently lacks the sophisticated adaptive learning features necessary to fully model individual learners, select the most effective learning approaches for each individual, or emulate the Zone of Proximal Development (ZPD) to the extent outlined in higher levels of personalized learning (PL) (Albdrani & Al-Shargabi, 2023).",
    "Achieving these capabilities would require significant advancements in AI, particularly in the areas of learner modeling, adaptive learning systems, and affective computing (Kocoń et al., 2023).",
    "In Fig. 1, the design of PL is based on the integration of various levels within the ChatGPT learning environment, which utilizes learner characteristics and dynamic behaviors to adapt instruction and customization."
  ]
}